Description: RGT is an open source Python 3.6+ library for analysis of regulatory genomics. RGT is programmed in an oriented object fashion and its core classes provide functionality for handling regulatory genomics data.
Home Page: https://github.com/CostaLab/reg-gen
Programs: rgt-TDF,rgt-THOR,rgt-hint,rgt-motifanalysis,rgt-viz

